name: Jellyfish Survival
description:
Help the Jellyfish survive in the deep water!

Play this fascinating game with high quality stunning designs where you have to slowly or quickly move to avoid the objects in your way. Reach the top!

How to play:

Tap to the right to swirl right
Tap to the left to swirl left
Tap the left and right quickly to move up straight

Features

• Stunning art
• Pleasant music
• Fun game play
• Many characters to choose from
